name: Joa
tagline: Java Library for Developing Microsoft Outlook Add-ins
body:
JOA - Java Library for Microsoft Outlook Addins
===

This library enables you to create an Addin for Microsoft Outlook with Java. 

Please follow this links to get more information:

- [JOA at WILUTIONS](www.wilutions.com/joa)
- [JOA Wiki](https://github.com/wolfgangimig/joa/wiki)
